{"tid":2068373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外交部長王毅敦促印度徹查印中邊境流血衝突肇事者","createTime":"2020-06-17T15:34:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T15:57:57.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e67fcc97d1a543639a2aad6dbf5bd4c5628347ac","tid":2068373,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:34:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.rfi.fr/media/display/4930f056-9dd3-11ea-ba06-005056a964fe/w:1280/p:16x9/53550297_101.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.rfi.fr%2Fmedia%2Fdisplay%2F4930f056-9dd3-11ea-ba06-005056a964fe%2Fw%3A1280%2Fp%3A16x9%2F53550297_101.jpg&h=c580ae28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據路透社說，王毅要求印方就中印邊界衝突開展徹查，嚴懲肇事責任人。<br />\n<br />\n外交部網站援引其同印度外長蘇傑生通電話的新聞稿並稱，雙方應通過中印邊界特別代表會晤機制、邊防部隊會晤機制等既有渠道，就妥處邊境事態加強溝通協調，共同維護邊境地區和平與安寧。據王毅稱，&ldquo;印方務必不要對當前形勢做出誤判，務必不要低估中方維護領土主權的堅定意志。&rdquo;王毅並強調，中印雙方相互尊重、相互支持是正道，符合兩國的長遠利益；相互猜忌、相互摩擦是邪路，違背兩國人民的根本願望。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.rfi.fr/cn/中國/20200617-中外交部官網稱王毅促印度徹查中印邊境流血衝突肇事者\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Fcn%2F%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%2F20200617-%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%83%A8%E5%AE%98%E7%B6%B2%E7%A8%B1%E7%8E%8B%E6%AF%85%E4%BF%83%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E5%BE%B9%E6%9F%A5%E4%B8%AD%E5%8D%B0%E9%82%8A%E5%A2%83%E6%B5%81%E8%A1%80%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81%E8%82%87%E4%BA%8B%E8%80%85&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4wRSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=a3677d39\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.rfi.fr/cn/中國/20200617-中外交部官網稱王毅促印度徹查中印邊境流血衝突肇事者</a>"},{"pid":"d715889a6f81d37476dc982d49b55670b1dc1432","tid":2068373,"uid":307619,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:35:11.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借位一用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">[全人類請入] 投訴蘇文隆 唔好再俾條粉皮害手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2068154\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2068154</a></span></span></strong><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rNPeQ2w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrNPeQ2w.jpg&h=f4a8a3f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suBXOPc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuBXOPc.jpg&h=39c942dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EdP2ZVS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEdP2ZVS.png&h=1bd9e71b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人會話法治已經死咗好撚耐<br />\n做呢啲嘢有撚用咩<br />\n<br />\n我唔知道做咗又冇用<br />\n我淨係知唔做就一定乜嘢都冇<br />\n<br />\n之前情操高尚嗰條粉皮暫時都冇得再審政治案件<br />\n都係多得各位手足堅持寫信投訴<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果唔想香港好嘅社工越來越少<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n得返一啲淨係識得幫新賤民呃公屋嘅社畜<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n未成年手足被藍屍社工出賣</span></span><br />\n唔該一人一信<br />\n保護一個為咗愛我地而失去左一年光陰<br />\n為咗愛香港而冒着釘牌危機都要行出嚟<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好懶<br />\n依家輪到我哋愛佢了"},{"pid":"dd7687e5ce1e6c34d5ecbb07616ae3f9920e9b2c","tid":2068373,"uid":154486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:39:11.000Z","msg":"干涉印度內政<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7fac3712ba3eadf1b486fc8ee9252f619f80984","tid":2068373,"uid":146285,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:40:18.000Z","msg":"印度：習近平"},{"pid":"fe4b3280e2fdc49178d5a00559551e4fcf1fb141","tid":2068373,"uid":34189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:41:45.000Z","msg":"邊境自己有份叫人查<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n廢唔廢d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83f3611078bc8cba31f21637ce36ca1efdfb9eb1","tid":2068373,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:41:52.000Z","msg":"印度人民想報仇喎  麻煩支共出兵啦喂  印度